beer.beer_description:
A fruity palate pleaser with a long lingering bitterness. Strong notes of mandarin & citrus.  
In Season IPA is aways brewed with the same base recipe but with the freshest hops from each hop harvest from the Northern Hemisphere and the Southern. This seasons hops are Southern Hemisphere In Season Hops: Enigma, Vic Secret, Helga, Australian Willamette & Galaxy.
This is also the last time Helga & Australian Willamette are being grown in Australia so we're giving them a good sendoff.

Read more here: http://4pinesbeer.com.au/our-beer/in-season-ipa/
